race.description: Roll The Dice Racing Mdn Plate
race.comment: NOBLE STEED (4) has been costly, going under when firm in the market in a few of his seven starts, but it took a good one to beat him last time out. He comfortably had the measure of a couple of his rivals here in that race. That was only third-up, so there's improvement to come and he'll relish this trip. LAST CARD LOUIE (2) is deep into a preparation that included some jumps racing in August but he found only one better in a stronger race than this last start so he only needs to hold his form to be a key player. The step up to 2400m presents a new challenge for NICOFFHOME (3) but he is racing too consistently to dismiss and might give them something to catch. BOLD TIMOTHY (1) also gets to 2400m for the first time but his racing style suggests he'll appreciate that trip. SONDER (5) could have more upside than most and will improve after two runs back from a spell.
